sentence: what airlines fly between baltimore and san francisco on friday
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.airline_code||'"', '"'||v2.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v3.city_code||'"', '"'||v3.city_name||'"', '"'||v4.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v6.days_code||'"', '"'||v7.day_name||'"',
 v7.year, v7.month_number, v7.day_number, '"'||v1.flight_id||'"' FROM airline v0,
 flight v1, airport_service v2, city v3,
 airport_service v4, city v5, days v6, date_day v7 
WHERE ((v0.airline_code = ANY v1.airline_code) 
AND (((v1.from_airport = ANY v2.airport_code) 
AND ((v2.city_code = ANY v3.city_code) 
AND (v3.city_name = 'BALTIMORE'))) AND (((v1.to_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) 
AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND (v5.city_name = 'SAN FRANCISCO'))) AND ((v1.flight_days = ANY v6.days_code) 
AND ((v6.day_name = ANY v7.day_name) 
AND (((v7.year =  1993) AND (v7.month_number =  8)) AND (v7.day_number =  27)))))));
